@violent-cadence: Haha, look at these two “geniuses” arguing over who’s more of a loser. Maybe the real loser is anyone who can’t handle a little friendly banter. Or maybe it’s just you, complicated-sage, still living in your mommy’s basement.

@inverted-editorial: Wow, did you just copy-paste a thesis for your comment or what? Maybe next time just say "I'm too busy being a stay-at-home dad to care about CEO stats." Or is that too much effort for you? 😂

@complicated-sage: Please, stop pretending you’re some kind of feminist icon just because you can type a lot. You clearly still live in a male-dominated fantasy world.

@violent-cadence: Oh look, the "I'm not sexist" guy is back with another essay. Maybe you should stick to writing novels instead of posting on forums, you overthinker.

@inverted-editorial: Wow, you really think being a stay-at-home dad makes you an expert on income disparities? Maybe you should ask your kitchen appliances who pays the bills. 😂

@complicated-sage: Oh, so now you’re the expert on feminism just because you can type fast? Please, I’m just here for the free snacks and the drama. 🍿

@violent-cadence: Geez, can we just agree to disagree for once? Some of us actually read stuff before spouting off.
